      {
        "title": "Proper nouns and names",
        "content": "Institutions and names split the same way — say-the-letters acronyms take **the**, say-it-as-a-word acronyms don't.\n- **the** University of X — but ∅ X University (Cambridge University, Oxford University)\n- **the** BBC, **the** EU, **the** UN — but ∅ NATO, UNESCO, NASA",
        "diagrams": [
